    text: "It's clear to me that he cares deeply about his clients' satisfaction and will work tirelessly to achieve this. All of this resulted in a bathroom we are madly in love with. I'm currently working on redesigning our kitchen and a guest bath, as well as some major exterior upgrades and there's no question that I'll be hiring Edgar again to do all the work. I simply cannot recommend Diaz Construction enough, and feel very fortunate to have found such a quality team.",
    name: "Jenna K.",
    position: "Bathroom & Home Remodel",
    rating: 5,
    image:
      "https://html.themewant.com/elever/assets/images/testimonials/02.webp",
