    text: "We recently asked Edgar to do a turf installation in our backyard. Edgar was extremely responsive and communicative, helped fit our budget, and executed the project quickly and on our schedule. Further he made some great design decisions that we really appreciate in hindsight versus our original ask. Our kids love the turf and have been out back every morning and afternoon since it was finished! Thanks Edgar!",
